public class AbstractGenericFactory<INPUT,OUTPUT,FAILURE extends Throwable>
extends Object
implements GenericFactory<INPUT,OUTPUT,FAILURE>

An abstract implementation of GenericFactory which provides default implementations for the factory methods. All default implementations throw an UnsupportedOperationException. Concrete factories are expected to override the methods they offer.

See GenericFactory
